<div style="text-align: justify;"> </div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">With the rescue diver course, you'll learn how to recognize and assist divers in need, no matter the situation. The largest issues typically involve panicking, unconscious, or otherwise unresponsive divers, all of which can prove to be a very daunting task for the unprepared rescuer. The rescue diver course provides the instruction and practice, you need to be comfortable and confident when helping a panicking or unconscious diver establish positive buoyancy, calming them, and getting them out of the water, and if necessary, performing rescue breaths while in the water, and CPR when on land or boat. 
</div>
<div><br />
</div>
