</h3>
<div><strong><em>Los Angeles, CA – May 9, 2014 -</em></strong> The feeling of gliding through a new world, one both older than the one you left behind on land and yet still new.   The feeling of slow motion flying, the sights of colorful schools of fish, or the mystery of the darkness of night underwater.   Feelings that few people know, but many wish to know.</div>
