<div style="text-align: justify;">Good jobs are difficult to find.  Finding good jobs that you also enjoy are even more so.   Finding these sorts of jobs means starting with what you already enjoy doing.  If you know and enjoy the experience of a world unlike ours, and also enjoy showing others this world, then teaching people how to dive or taking them on trips into this world might be for you. </div>
