<div><br />
</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">An <a href="http://www.malibudivers.com/sections/open-water-scuba-instructor" target="_blank" title="PADI IDC">Instructor Development Course</a> (IDC) is the cornerstone of PADI's professional-level training that can result in earning your Assistant Instructor rating and qualify a you to attend the Instructor Examination to earn your PADI Open Water Scuba Instructor (OWSI).  IDC’s are offered periodically and privately. The next IDC will be held at Malibu Divers on <a href="http://www.malibudivers.com/calendar" target="_blank" title="Next IDC">May 28th</a>. 
</div>
